sed during the current session of use. This is especially helpful in knowing whether your grilling surface is maintaining its temperature adequately or if temperature fluctuations are causing your food to cook poorly. To conserve battery life, the device shuts off automatically after 10 minutes of inactivity.","For at-home cooks in need of a portable and simple BBQ thermometer, the Epica Ultra-Fast Digital Meat Thermometer is a popular choice. Its compact design combined with its wide temperature reading range make for a helpful and reliable product. While it does have a slight issue with accuracy, it still performs well in giving quick temperature readings with minimal waiting times."]},"id":"de786cda-df45-4410-b5cb-a89e626e04c7","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_60110","url":"/epica-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"linda-thomson","url":"/author/linda-thomson","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Linda Thomson","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"SD7AJ8PTDFstvquABQDpsH","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-07-31T21:20:45Z","datePublished":"2014-07-31T21:20:45Z","name":"Epica Ultra-Fast Digital Meat Thermometer ES432","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Digital Grill Thermometers here.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Digital Grill Thermometers here.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-07-31T21:20:45Z","id":"GbD4bMunjuY4AnV5cyzsV7","meta":{"title":"Epica Ultra-Fast Digital Meat Thermometer ES432 Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Epica Ultra-Fast Digital Meat